{"tid":1758260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"12月5號法國大罷工","createTime":"2019-11-27T02:48:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T03:04:51.000Z","uid":264183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6d0dfe9c30e9c1903923a40f128ba787e3cd2e0d","tid":1758260,"uid":264183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:48:33.000Z","msg":"收到公司消息話法國12月5號號會有個<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">全國大罷工</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n全個法國會玩和你塞，機場會停運作<br />\n暫定一日，但唔知會唔會持續<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nNow here we are with a national and wide strike on the 5th of December.<br />\nRoads might be blocked by drivers, might stop the traffic, post and airport staff as well may stop working ++++<br />\nWe expect the demonstration only for one day but it might be renewed if the government response is not in accordance with the demand of the nation or French labours. French unions are also involved and it might cause stronger impulse to the strike.<br />\n<br />\n我哋有冇得喺香港一齊聲援？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef2d15552e8cfbe15c7ef4e2a42559dc0f92af1a","tid":1758260,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:52:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QWeEy2B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQWeEy2B.png&h=90138a27&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fgsiPAW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfgsiPAW.png&h=78ef3435&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n怕香港人善忘嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n想聲援理大手足嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n和理非嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n勇武嘅，推行動 post 啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係行動post，星期三晚，我地聚首商場，以和理非聲援理大手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756593\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756593</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b094f4123c06b4c9ccbb42c26ad5e2657ba90b92","tid":1758260,"uid":264183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:53:22.000Z","msg":"自推10下"},{"pid":"406585c3288367691de49be415785b22524a5c73","tid":1758260,"uid":264183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:54:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"90dc068b79a23fd8ba387f8012343c34d4cc2044","tid":1758260,"uid":264183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:54:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"29f03020ecfde2f690f76e8a6ed708ea0ec27750","tid":1758260,"uid":264183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:55:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b86144b0c56e3433e601c44575f2f46a01a389f6","tid":1758260,"uid":264183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:55:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"42ab5e98b6b54426228083f0e56c9ff4124f01d5","tid":1758260,"uid":264183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:56:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cea84e75fb4e522a49606f3c6a20f39a9d57fafe","tid":1758260,"uid":264183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:56:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"25e5a31be29886f7c86cc77639fc5e3018b54a52","tid":1758260,"uid":264183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:56:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ee446b85e2802f797ebb58dbdd27fce6f43a02a3","tid":1758260,"uid":264183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:57:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5aff733abb138085bed1f3cd8d8fdf756c910854","tid":1758260,"uid":264183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:57:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ec703f1718ab80d2dd75c75dbca418ea1d8cb379","tid":1758260,"uid":264183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:58:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7272379f2b1fad50baaa4cd3ac2b21e1523211cf","tid":1758260,"uid":266755,"like":0,"d